title: Edguy - 2005 - Superheroes [320kbs] ~~Renovatio~~
description:
Superheroes is an EP by the German power metal band Edguy, released in 2005. Michael Kiske of Helloween has a guest appearance. On this EP, the band has moved away from the sound they had developed on their previous album Hellfire Club. The songs on "Superheroes" are much less akin to the band's native style of power metal, but tends towards the direction of hard rock.
